creator: Rene Werner
descriptionHtml:
The orc tribes gather to take over the world. Take your heroes and stop them.

Train your group of heroes and face various adventures.


- Explore a campaign for orcs

- Defeat other players in the arena

- Explore the dark tower and get useful gifts

- Found your own guild and defeat strong opponents together

- Daily new raid opponents
